<div id="hero" class="">
  <section class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-7">
        <h1>A Different Parts Search</h1>
        <p>Whatever you are looking for, the Parts Ninja will help you find it! The Parts Ninja cross references thousands of parts to find you every possible compatible option.</p>
        <div class="cta">
          <%= link_to icon(:play) + " Learn More", "#about", class: "btn-outline popup-media" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-5">
        <%= image_tag("landing/ThePartsNinjaMockUp.png", class:"fadeInScale hidden-xs") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div id="stats" class="">
  <div class="container">
    <ul class="stats-list">
      <li class="stat">50,000+ Vehicles</li>
      <li class="stat">300,000+ Parts</li>
      <li class="stat">Millions of Possibilities</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="intro" class="index-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h3>How does it actually work?</h3>
      <p>
        The Parts Ninja has both a web app and an android app to make your website easy and always available. It offers you all the designs in collaboration with some smart people. Your projects will look great everywhere you go.
      </p>
    </header>
    <section class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h4>Take all your photos at all times</h4>
        <p>
          The Parts Ninja is the perfect solution for web developers and designers. You can get an awesome website for your best projects and clients, and also get support for any questions and matters that you might have.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h4>Upgrade your account to get all features</h4>
        <p>
          The Parts Ninja is designed to make showing off your best projects extremely fast and simple. There are many ways to configure. Just go to the source, make changes and the rest is taken care automatically.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h4>You have options...</h4>
    <h1>Let the Parts Ninja find them</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="search-types" class="index-search-types">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="title">
      <h2>Two unique ways of searching</h2>
      <p>
        Other websites will show you information about a part but they stop there.
        The Parts Ninja takes it a step further and will give you detailed analysis on compatibilities and fitment.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row search-type">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <%= image_tag("landing/Basic_Search.png", class:"img-responsive") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h3>
          Find Compatibilities
        </h3>
        <p>
          Built to find compatibile vehicles that share a specfic part. Perfect for when the part you need is unavailable,
          and all your other options have been exhausted.
        </p>
        <%= link_to icon(:chevron_right) + " Find Compatibilities", find_index_path, class: "btn-rounded" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row search-type">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6 col-xs-12">
        <%= image_tag("landing/Discovery_example.png", class:"img-responsive devices") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6 col-xs-12 column-right">
        <h3>Check Compatibility
        </h3>
        <p>
          Need to see if the part you grabbed will fit? Perfect for those times you see a great deal but are unsure
          it'll work for your vehicle.
        </p>
        <%= link_to icon(:chevron_right) + " Check Compatibility", check_index_path, class: "btn-rounded" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="index-features-files mobile-alt clearfix">
  <div class="container2">
    <div class="container1">
      <div class="col col-left">
        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature clearfix">
            <div class="image">
              <%= icon(:earth) %>
            </div>
            <div class="info">
              <strong>
                Save Money
              </strong>
              <p>
                Many times there are alternative parts that are fractions the cost of the main brand. In some cases these
                are even rebranded and sold for more!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature clearfix">
            <div class="image">
              <%= icon(:earth) %>
            </div>
            <div class="info">
              <strong>
                Save Time
              </strong>
              <p>
                Finding used and specialty parts can be time consuming. Unless your Google-foo skills are up to stuff,
                it can take hours to find alternative parts and/or fitment information.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col col-right">
        <div class="info">
          <h3>Get Updates</h3>
          <h4>
            Open registration isn't open yet, but will be soon!
          </h4>
          <p>
            The Parts Ninja will not soley rely on existing data, we want to know your discoveries! Your input will build
            out the compatibility web for future users. Sign up for the email list and you'll receive early user invivation
            special offers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="index-features-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <section>
      <div class="info">
        <strong>
          Ready to get started and be awesome?
        </strong>
        <%= simple_form_for @lead, html: { class: "form-inline"} do |f| %>
          <%= f.input :email, label: false, placeholder: "Your Email" %>
          <%= f.button :button, wrapper_html: { class: "input-group-btn"}, class: "btn btn-default" do %>
            <%= icon(:chevron_right) %>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
